snippet.title: PlayStation - Simple 1500 Series Vol 008 - The Solitaire (1998)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
The Solitaire is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Success and published by Chat Noir, which was released in Japan in 1998.
